《'''追尋人生'''》（{{lang-en|''Chasing Life''}}）是[[ABC家庭|ABC Family]] 2014年6月10日於黃金時段開播的美國影集。<ref name="ABC Family Summer">{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2014/03/10/abc-family-announces-summer-premiere-dates-for-pretty-little-liars-switched-at-birth-chasing-life-mystery-girls-chasing-life/243459/ |title=ABC Family Announces Summer Premiere Dates for 'Pretty Little Liars', 'Switched at Birth' 'Chasing Life', 'Mystery Girls' & 'Young & Hungry' |last=Kondolojy |first=Amanda |publisher=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]] |date=2014-03-10 |accessdate=2014-03-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/08/14/abc-family-starts-production-on-new-drama-series-chasing-life-125112/20130814abcfamily01/ |title=Breaking News - ABC Family Starts Production on New Drama Series "Chasing Life" |publisher=[[ABC家庭|ABC Family]] via [[The_Futon_Critic|The Futon Critic]] |date=2013-08-14 |accessdate=2013-10-03}}</ref>本劇改編自墨西哥[[Televisa|Televisa電視台]]製作的西班牙語電視劇《''Terminales''》。<ref>{{cite web |first=Billy |last=Nilles |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2013/04/abc-family-orders-chasing-life-to-series.html |title=ABC Family orders ‘Chasing Life’ to series |publisher=[[Zap2it|Zap2it]] |date=2013-04-24 |accessdate=2013-10-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140215090110/http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2013/04/abc-family-orders-chasing-life-to-series.html |archivedate=2014-02-15 }}</ref><ref name="Terminales picked up">{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/abc-family-pilot-terminales-picked-up-to-series-titled-chasing-life/ |title=ABC Family Pilot 'Terminales' Picked Up - Titled 'Chasing Life' |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2013-04-24 |accessdate=2013-10-03}}</ref>本劇最初預定13集，2013年11月27日，宣布追加7集，因此第一季預定將有20集。<ref>{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/11/abc-family-chasing-life-back-order/ |title=ABC Family’s ‘Chasing Life’ Gets Back Order Ahead Of Premiere |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2013-11-27 |accessdate=2013-11-28}}</ref>2014年7月15日，ABC Family宣布第一季後半段的集數（ep 11-20）將於2015年播出，並再追加一集聖誕特輯，第一季預定21集。

2014年11月6日，ABC Family宣布續訂第二季。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/abc-familys-chasing-life-renewed-746957|title=ABC Family's 'Chasing Life' Renewed for Second Season|author=Lesley Goldberg|work=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]}}</ref>2015年10月2日，ABC Family宣布取消本劇。<ref name="hollywoodreporter.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/chasing-life-canceled-abc-family-828994|title='Chasing Life' canceled ABC Family|work=好萊塢報導}}</ref>

== 故事 ==
講述24歲的四月，是個聰明、機伶有抱負的記者，她努力地想要一步一步的爬向波士頓日報裡更高的位子；而四月仍需在家庭與工作中取得平衡。正當四月的事業、家庭與愛情看似漸漸轉好的時候，她卻從擔任醫生的叔叔口中，得知自己罹患癌症的悲慘消息。

